                        S. Batik
                    </th>
                    <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wider">
                        S. Olahraga
                    </th>
                    <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wider">
                        S. Muslim
                    </th>
                    <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wider">
                        Topi
                    </th>
